Class Union

      • unionFixed

        public static <E> java.util.Set<E> unionFixed​(java.util.Collection<? extends E> a,
                                              java.util.Collection<? extends E> b)
        Fixed collection union method.
        Type Parameters:
        E - The type of elements maintained by the collections.
        Parameters:
        a - A Collection of objects.
        b - Another Collection of objects.
        Returns:
        A Set containing the union of a and b excluding null elements;
        A Set containing the elements of the other collection if either of the parameters are null;
        A empty Set if both parameters are null.
